<AFF>Fungus Testing Laboratory<BR>University of Texas Health Science Center<BR>San Antonio, Texas<BR>&ast;Phone: (780) 987-4811<BR>Fax: (780) 987-4141<BR>E-mail: lynne.sigler&commat;ualberta.ca</AFF>
